14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
16 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 17-116.23 of Title 70, unless
17 there is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
18 Any person receiving benefits from the Teachers' Retirement
19 System of Oklahoma as of June 30, 2025, who continues to receive
20 benefits on or after July 1, 2025, and whose maximum compensation
21 level was limited to Twenty-five Thousand Dollars ($25,000.00) at
22 the time of retirement shall, for purposes of the benefit amount
23 payable to such person on or after the effective date of this act,
24 have the original retirement benefit amount payable to the member at
